RSA Encryption/Decryption

To build executable on *nix systems type:
 $ make Rsa-crypt

 1. Generate keys g /home/vorlov/CLionProjects/rsa/public_key /home/vorlov/CLionProjects/rsa/private_key

 2. Encrypt data e /home/vorlov/CLionProjects/rsa/source_message.txt /home/vorlov/CLionProjects/rsa/encrypted_message.txt /home/vorlov/CLionProjects/rsa/public_key

 3. Decrypt data d /home/vorlov/CLionProjects/rsa/encrypted_message.txt /home/vorlov/CLionProjects/rsa/decrypted_message.txt /home/vorlov/CLionProjects/rsa/private_key

 ./rsa g /home/vorlov/CLionProjects/rsa/public_key /home/vorlov/CLionProjects/rsa/private_key

 ./rsa e /home/vorlov/CLionProjects/rsa/source_message.txt /home/vorlov/CLionProjects/rsa/encrypted_message.txt /home/vorlov/CLionProjects/rsa/public_key

 ./rsa d /home/vorlov/CLionProjects/rsa/encrypted_message.txt /home/vorlov/CLionProjects/rsa/decrypted_message.txt /home/vorlov/CLionProjects/rsa/private_key